  "title": "🍹 Bartender – Immediate Hiring (Junior / Senior)",
  "description": "<p>📍 Location: Tanjong Pagar</p><p>💰 Salary: $2,500 – $3,000<br /></p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>- Assist in daily bar operations and opening/closing procedures</p><p>- Serve drinks and cocktails efficiently, providing smooth guest service</p><p>- Greet and interact with guests, recommend drinks, explain specials and seasonal items</p><p>- Maintain bar cleanliness, stock levels, and equipment</p><p>- Support inventory management and assist with supplier relations</p><p>- Learn and grow skills under senior staff guidance; opportunity to develop classic and signature cocktails</p><p>- Rotate to floor service duties when required</p><p>- Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned<br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>- 1+ year bartending experience (Junior) | 3+ years (Senior)</p><p>- Proficient in mixing cocktails and beverage service</p><p>- Friendly, positive, and excellent customer service skills</p><p>- Team player, well-organised, and able to communicate effectively</p><p>- Keen to learn and cross-train, able to cover shifts as required<br /></p><p>✨ Grow your bartending career with hands-on training and a dynamic team!<br /></p><p>How to Apply:</p><p>📞 WhatsApp: wa.me/6589387313<br /></p><p>Send with Code: <strong>BARTENDER</strong> + these details:</p><p>✅ Full Name</p><p>✅ Residential Area</p><p>✅ Earliest Availability Date</p><p>✅ Commitment Period</p><p>✅ Able to work on weekends? (Y/N)</p><p>✅ Attach Resume</p><p>And please attached a copy of your resume</p><p>https://t.me/sgbesttempjobs</p><p>https://t.me/varioustempjobs<br /></p><p>Chia Xin Ee Crystal | R21103390</p><p>EA License No: 21C0626</p>",
